Home
  
In the heart of nature’s arms,
I find a place still and free,
Where moments meld into dreams,
And whispers of life become me.

Sky and earth in quiet embrace,
Mountain and river, bird and tree,
All weave together in harmony,
Echoing eternity's decree.

- Ruth Dallas
